{"tid":613599,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：劉子頎被浸大罰停學1學期 陳樂行停學8日","createTime":"2018-04-01T19:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T16:01:48.000Z","uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89677ae5b1c746b57f27e3c78a1ec6f0f7a6d94f","tid":613599,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:06:15.000Z","msg":"消息指，浸大決定，學生會前會長劉子頎就「佔領語文中心」行動，罰停學1個學期；中醫藥學院學生陳樂行停學8日，及需要在校內進行40小時服務。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩人亦需要撰寫道歉信。另外，由於兩人早前曾被停課，紀律委員會將當陳樂行已完成停課的懲處。<br />\n<br />\n陳樂行回覆本台查詢時表示，已決定上訴，認為紀律聆訊的程序有嚴重問題，但詳細情況將留待記者會上交代。至於劉子頎就暫時未能聯絡到。<br />\n<br />\n一批浸大學生因不滿校方的普通話豁免試評分標準不透明，今年一月曾參與「佔領語文中心」行動，其中劉子頎及陳樂行一度被暫時停學，校內有師生遊行抗議校方做法。劉子頎及陳樂行向語文中心教職員道歉後，校方其後撤銷兩人的停學令，以等待紀律委員會的決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1389075-20180401.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1389075-20180401.htm&d=ydmL7MEAMtVscdTyxdshVZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=b80c8650\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1389075-20180401.htm&h=27c85731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1389075-20180401.htm</a>"},{"pid":"050406e91f91015673980238a34e8704148126b6","tid":613599,"uid":38316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"又話唔罰又話罰<br />\n彈弓手到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1086db4d7dc4bf204d62189d7e7f927f2d2fcd","tid":613599,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:03:33.000Z","msg":"冷處理一陣, 然後罰你就冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30577d6da744fc8e873688d46a224e5c66c1a09e","tid":613599,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"